12-15 Brussle Sprouts
1/2 cup Crasins
1/2 cup roasted+salted pistashio
1/2 minced shallot
3 pickeld hot cherry pepper - diced
olive oil
fine balsamic vinegar

pick off leaves of sprouts and blanch for 2 minutes in a hot water. Toss with other ingredients. Salt and pepper to taste. Serve with fresh parmisean di parma shavings.
